    <string name="onboarding_p1_title">Taimakon ƙwararre a aljihunka</string>
    <string name="onboarding_p1_body">Mira na\'urar bincike ce da ke duba hoton mahaifa tare da kai kuma ta ba da shawarar ko a kai mai jinya wajen ƙwararre. Hukuncin likitanci yana hannunka.</string>
    <string name="onboarding_p2_title">Matakai uku masu sauƙi</string>
    <string name="onboarding_p2_body">Shirya mai jinya kuma matse sau ɗaya. Mira tana ɗaukar hotuna uku da sauri a jere, ta zaɓi mafi tsabta, kuma ta nuna shawara tare da kima na tabbas. Kai ne ka yanke shawara abin yi na gaba.</string>
    <string name="onboarding_p3_title">Sirrinka a farko</string>
    <string name="onboarding_p3_body">Hotunan masu jinya suna kasancewa a wannan wayar. Mira ba ta tura su ko\'ina sai dai idan ka zaɓi haka.</string>
