    <string name="help_heatmap_title">Mene ne taswirar zafin?</string>
    <string name="help_heatmap_body">Launi da aka rufe yana nuna inda Mira ta duba lokacin yanke shawara. Wuraren da suke haske sune yankunan da Mira ta ɗauka muhimmanci. Idan wurin haske ya faɗi a kan mahaifa kuma ya yi daidai da abin da kake gani a matsayin acetowhite, sakamakon ya fi amincewa. Idan ya faɗi a kan speculum ko wani wuri, ka yi taka tsantsan da sakamakon kuma ka yi tunanin sake ɗaukar hoto.</string>
    <string name="help_confidence_title">Mene ne ma\'anar tabbas?</string>
    <string name="help_confidence_body">Tabbas shine yadda Mira take da tabbas game da amsarta, daga 0 zuwa 100%%. Sama da 80%% yana da ƙarfi. Ƙasa da matakin da kuka saita a Saituna (tsoho 65%%), Mira za ta sanya sakamakon a matsayin bai tabbata ba kuma ta nemi sake hoto. Hukuncinka na likitanci yana da muhimmanci fiye da lambar.</string>
